Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.68,0:22:47.87,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}見慣れない街の中に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:53.21,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}陷入迷茫的心
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.87,0:22:53.21,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}迷い込んだ気持ちをただ
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.21,0:23:03.47,EDCN,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}只想寻找能将我引导至出口的双手
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.21,0:23:03.47,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}出口へ導く手を探していたの
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.47,0:23:07.46,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\be20\fade(300,300)}Wherever you are I'll find you
